{"tid":1467401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嘈乜鳩民意，認清自己爭取既野。 唔批准五大訴求，我哋要攬炒呀！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:56:13.000Z","uid":43785,"like":14,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e473da2b5afb7757fc565d6ba2c22b4af24d35","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:29.000Z","msg":"機場旅客開始對「香港示威者」感到不滿？訪問下英國法國機場罷工時啲旅客點睇，人哋有冇care過你哋？佢哋只會care自己爭取到啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀你哋諗清楚啦！<br />\n民意有乜撚嘢用， 民意係用嚟畀班議員爭取選票用， 唔係畀我哋用嚟爭取五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n我哋依家係希望癱瘓機場， 用攬炒既方式迫使政府答應我哋五大訴求， 既然講到係攬炒就唔好care民意。<br />\n<br />\n200萬人行出嚟， 即使係搞到香港咁撚亂都咁多人同團體支持我地， 根本就唔需要理咁多， 想做乜就做乜， 講撚咗話核彈都唔割就唔割架啦， 咪畀啲傻閪帶風向啦。<br />\n<br />\n其實政府嗰度得班警察支持㗎咋，仲講民意？醒未呀連登仔。 班議員用嚟呃選票㗎咋。"},{"pid":"de50b48d7e369bc8481830cc6bb3e59306f4f335","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:06.000Z","msg":"塞旅客就一定要塞，如果唔係出機場做咩？塞嘅話，留返一個counter出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。"},{"pid":"3e775f7b50559d927a446e49a976f0dc93e75b78","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"班藍絲最大既優點，佢地就真係核彈都唔割啦！睇到扮睇唔到，黑講成白，盲撐黑警。早一日和理非仲話核彈都唔割，又話攬炒唔驚，講就聲大大，阻下個旅客上機已經鳩屌，圍個公安就話割。嗌入機場要人還眼個陣唔係好口響咩？而家捉到隻臥底就愛心大爆發話打夠放人啦?"},{"pid":"364878b45105f12ca7b5ae53783eb901e11de620","tid":1467401,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"道歉大行動，你我有責<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民間記者會要AM開，先道歉，多次，先壓住輿論</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3日唔入機場，唔係輸曬外媒<br />\n而且而家文宣需要大量人手<br />\n3日唔入機場，睇左風向壓唔壓得住先<br />\n星期六仲要保護老師，對付福建幫"},{"pid":"4ba7e03f5e0b74566775f0f07f805989777b1a36","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"癱瘓機場兩日都係集會做成，只不過一日人多一日人少。琴日因為人塞滿所以停，今日係坐係離境位所以停。只係觀感上唔同，但事實係一樣，依家其實問題係想去宣傳定癱瘓，宣傳唔適合太多人入去，因為人多一定會做成阻塞。所以唔該搞清楚到底入機場目的係宣傳定癱瘓。"},{"pid":"96f489ae348dcc7cef9a4b5dc4c17bae76da530e","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ba7e03f5e0b74566775f0f07f805989777b1a36","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"癱瘓機場兩日都係集會做成，只不過一日人多一日人少。琴日因為人塞滿所以停，今日係坐係離境位所以停。只係觀感上唔同，但事實係一樣，依家其實問題係想去宣傳定癱瘓，宣傳唔適合太多人入去，因為人多一定會做成阻塞。所以唔該搞清楚到底入機場目的係宣傳定癱瘓。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"旅客只會諗到因為你塞爆，佢先被迫停。所以塞爆個機場同交通令政府機管局取消航班，同走去塞住個入口唔俾人走，一樣係阻到人。想唔阻到人當初就咪話入機場升級塞爆佢，入得就咪又要威又要戴頭盔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70622dc299fe071d4c0e2091777ecba59862d30","tid":1467401,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1280d812a31c6787f35bf7d7eb481b93d181111","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:01.000Z","msg":"有冷血軍師吹風，話塞機場但唔好阻到人。好心你啦，依家係不合作運動，阻人係一定。世上冇不合作運動係唔阻人，如果你要唔麻煩人，咁你塞乜鬼機場？最基本航班停止就會阻到人啦！同佔領個時啲左膠話佔路但唔好阻人返工有乜分別？"},{"pid":"e2405030d7f9c15f013f456ac0121b0030c3bbd4","tid":1467401,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"請大家入機場前備戰、坐公共交通前就要上裝<br />\n防cctv 因為會有機會好似今日咁打狗救手足<br />\n口罩、帽，仲有耳仔<br />\n全黑衣服、飲水、食野請小心"},{"pid":"b9e5775f737cfeb2aa65897382c563e6cc73dc67","tid":1467401,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"認同 唔狙擊你了"},{"pid":"d8acb7c408d2f6eb3bb068de945173398989e04a","tid":1467401,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:52.000Z","msg":"鳩蛇未收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241960067f2d687f1db5359db5df36a7927812f5","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非回合？成件事好自相矛盾，咁係咪如果有義士勇武，和理非就會割席。咁既然唔割，做咩唔比勇武？</span></span><br />\n事實上，網絡出現大量勇武行動係黑警賊喊捉賊，甚至叫抗爭者見到激進行為就捉鬼，結果就返到雨革時代，邊個衝邊個係鬼，大量左膠出沒阻頭阻勢，最怕社運就此結束。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dd412e605e15f07e690b0f087718b86785e5d6","tid":1467401,"uid":274994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir,失去民心嘅話，比街坊屌嘅就係我地啦"},{"pid":"1b9bdf7cf3f0de08e90d40fc66b6d3fe858c1c21","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"364878b45105f12ca7b5ae53783eb901e11de620","tid":1467401,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"道歉大行動，你我有責<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民間記者會要AM開，先道歉，多次，先壓住輿論</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3日唔入機場，唔係輸曬外媒<br />\n而且而家文宣需要大量人手<br />\n3日唔入機場，睇左風向壓唔壓得住先<br />\n星期六仲要保護老師，對付福建幫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"道乜嘢？<br />\n咪撚搞到班示威者好似有錯咁樣！<br />\n警察亂開槍出嚟道咗歉未？<br />\n警察冇帶委任證出嚟道歉未？<br />\n<br />\n幾時輪到班後生仔出嚟道歉？<br />\n輿論用嚟做乜鳩！<br />\n當政府都唔用唔care嘅時候你點解要理？<br />\n咪撚畀政黨利用啦"},{"pid":"f0bcf10697632ba79359dc7ed7ae45e4157653aa","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75dd412e605e15f07e690b0f087718b86785e5d6","tid":1467401,"uid":274994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:26.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir,失去民心嘅話，比街坊屌嘅就係我地啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"你都痴線， 亂撚咗兩個月呀， 啲街坊有冇屌鳩你呀"},{"pid":"5174cdd35fac80fa6cc4aca14a52cab5d0727957","tid":1467401,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"「軍規」唔想今晚機場嘅嘢重演同我入哂嚟!!!!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467593</a>"},{"pid":"47f37788a616cf4475dd72e4be371c861e64a5f0","tid":1467401,"uid":51618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e775f7b50559d927a446e49a976f0dc93e75b78","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"班藍絲最大既優點，佢地就真係核彈都唔割啦！睇到扮睇唔到，黑講成白，盲撐黑警。早一日和理非仲話核彈都唔割，又話攬炒唔驚，講就聲大大，阻下個旅客上機已經鳩屌，圍個公安就話割。嗌入機場要人還眼個陣唔係好口響咩？而家捉到隻臥底就愛心大爆發話打夠放人啦?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8550dd08c2ab32560fc7d0570041f5ec912e2fe4","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e775f7b50559d927a446e49a976f0dc93e75b78","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:25.000Z","msg":"班藍絲最大既優點，佢地就真係核彈都唔割啦！睇到扮睇唔到，黑講成白，盲撐黑警。早一日和理非仲話核彈都唔割，又話攬炒唔驚，講就聲大大，阻下個旅客上機已經鳩屌，圍個公安就話割。嗌入機場要人還眼個陣唔係好口響咩？而家捉到隻臥底就愛心大爆發話打夠放人啦?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CSxPdp4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCSxPdp4.jpg&h=aff62d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暈倒既公安上救護車後立即張開眼醒番。<br />\n<br />\n恭喜各位大愛和理非，成功幫助敵人逃走了，不失民心不中計了，高興嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4539e5f8fb43131adb9ea23c6025a02248496a5","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尋日就有散水黨，今日就有民意黨，聽日係咪會有休養黨？</span></span>"},{"pid":"bec7f34e578c120cc89b4cc8dc75349dbe93119d","tid":1467401,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbb0836d260ad28751ffab7870c6a6d9bd2814ae","tid":1467401,"uid":41099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"好有POINT <br />\n幫推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非回合？成件事好自相矛盾，咁係咪如果有義士勇武，和理非就會割席。咁既然唔割，做咩唔比勇武？<br />\n事實上，網絡出現大量勇武行動係黑警賊喊捉賊，甚至叫抗爭者見到激進行為就捉鬼，結果就返到雨革時代，邊個衝邊個係鬼，大量左膠出沒阻頭阻勢，最怕社運就此結束。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"58490b0ed5b2195692d0ff5a38d1f8e2bbab6427","tid":1467401,"uid":264780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"我哋要嘅唔係民意<br />\n而係有冇<span style=\"color: red;\">打擊主要對手</span><br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">誰是我們的敵人？誰是我們的朋友？</span>這個問題是革命的首要問題。中國過去一切革命鬥爭<span style=\"color: red;\">成效甚少</span>，其基本原因就是因為不能<span style=\"color: red;\">團結真正的朋友，以攻擊真正的敵人。</span>革命黨是群眾的嚮導，在革命中未有革命黨領錯了路而革命不失敗的。我們的革命要有不領錯路和一定成功的把握，不可不注意<span style=\"color: red;\">團結我們的真正的朋友，以攻擊我們的真正的敵人。</span>我們要分辨真正的敵友，不可不將中國社會各階級的經濟地位及其對於革命的態度，作一個大概的分析。」<br />\n毛澤東<br />\n《中國社會各階級的分析》<br />\n1926 年<br />\n<br />\n機場旅客係咪我哋嘅敵人<br />\n定係可以團結嘅朋友？"},{"pid":"706a389e5712f165d397e9829a88109846c7c0ed","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d663e2c200e0e78464e9a230e15307f9fb745be9","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知道有啲嘢講中咗， 有啲人唔願意推<br />\n我自己推囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b82ae5685fa074e68154c2e00226e2a39965ca1","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9e5775f737cfeb2aa65897382c563e6cc73dc67","tid":1467401,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"認同 唔狙擊你了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:25.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704da565104e1a1c3e9f170b6fa3412da9783a56","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2405030d7f9c15f013f456ac0121b0030c3bbd4","tid":1467401,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"請大家入機場前備戰、坐公共交通前就要上裝<br />\n防cctv 因為會有機會好似今日咁打狗救手足<br />\n口罩、帽，仲有耳仔<br />\n全黑衣服、飲水、食野請小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f13eaac44de8ec1930dc9614d1bca211324868d","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20846f8ec62241fe747fb563fc4b6f442bebfac","tid":1467401,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:04:20.000Z","msg":"遇鬼時<br />\n<br />\n1）先捉，<br />\n<br />\n2）圍大圈，分隔 同比多d 記者同人映隻鬼，<br />\n<br />\n個個企到密，根本映唔到。<br />\n<br />\n如鬼或自己人有受傷，都要拍片搵在場醫護幫忙<br />\n<br />\n自己傷固之然要醫護， 亦要係記者前問鬼有冇受傷或身體不適，搵在場醫護幫忙做初步檢查，盡番人道立場同道德高地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）搵記者影記錄，重點指出隻鬼做左乜野犯罪行為如打人，煽動，藏有危險品之類，所以採訪101拘捕令。<br />\n<br />\n有物證就映埋物證。同令佢身分曝光，唔好祈望隻鬼會自爆，如果你諗住全世界鏡頭前嚴刑迫供，咁根本係另類送人頭，更何況打死隻鬼，相信佢都唔會講。<br />\n<br />\n闡明你嘅行為係合法性同正當性，同有需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）同時搵議員，叫議員處理/議員報警處理。<br />\n相信10多其9都上白車，popo都放人。<br />\n<br />\n重點係，你留住隻鬼冇乜用，只會令現場仲難控制仲亂，好似今日咁，好易比其他鬼去分化，阻醫護阻記者，<br />\n<br />\n如只做1-4，我知大家可能會好嬲，想發洩，但係隻鬼重點係要佢曝光比世界，囉資料，囉更多頻譜，依個先更有利。<br />\n<br />\n你唔好忘記一舉一動既然係鏡頭前，就要有鏡頭禮儀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒有最好的方法，要有改善的辦法"},{"pid":"8176ffc6303750a948e710129ab1ca02657cd553","tid":1467401,"uid":137688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMczpKv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMczpKv.png&h=eb765322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家不推文回覆"},{"pid":"7647f378291b0ee7d02d7071b7784b29814bddf5","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:15:35.000Z","msg":"吸取前車之鑑，團結不割席，不指責"},{"pid":"6bb918674817a6a4f7832df58c39e9a335c944f0","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bec7f34e578c120cc89b4cc8dc75349dbe93119d","tid":1467401,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:57.000Z","msg":"吸取前車之鑑，團結不割席，不指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe7ce54ae8520246a417ba18b0685d1e9a7b45d","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc005d2377db2596087da725ecde0d58aa4fe59","tid":1467401,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4ddd463b802860cc76a60d4dc5404ac7ecd3eb","tid":1467401,"uid":46038,"like":0,"dis